snippet.title: Amber Scott Testimonial for Gagan Sarkaria
snippet.description:
Check out Amber’s journey with Gagan as she gains “Ambitious Clarity” and “Brilliant Breakthroughs” to create her Personal & Systematic Blueprint of Success via her SoulCode & LifeMap. As she moves forward to creating her extraordinary soul-rich life and business she’s excited to create her wealth and financial freedom through my elite MoneyCode coaching program. 

(Ambitious Clarity is having an understanding of clear pathway to your purposeful ambitions in life.)
